java.util.Observer
public class Level5
extends Map
implements java.util.Observer

This class is the "level5" map for the campaign mode of tanks. It contains a unique ItemCreator and a preset locations to place the obstacles, PlayerTank, and the EnemyTank.

Team Exception

setUpMap

public void setUpMap()
This method actually sets up the predetermined map that has been designed as seen below. It will include adding all the five different obstacles onto the map including immovable blocks, crates, fire rings, TNT, and spike pits.
